
'''* Article: The culture of the socioeconomy of solidarity. Marcos Arruda. Article prepared for the Brazilian meeting on “Culture of the Socioeconomy of solidarity” - Rio de Janeiro, June 2000.'''


URL = http://base.socioeco.org/docs/doc-7281_en.pdf

=Summary=

"A variety of concepts of « culture » exists, such as that of the culture of cooperation and solidarity that, according to the author, is also one of love. Marcos Arruda attempts to adapt the notion of culture to socioeconomy. In the culture of globalized modernity, the notion of « economy » has been distorted changing from « home management » to « accumulation of wealth »."
(http://socioeco.org/bdf/en/corpus_document/fiche-document-1266.html)


